## ✨ Features

- Unique draw-based movement system using a pencil mechanic  
- Real-time monster eraser AI that chases the player  
- Dynamic path creation that affects gameplay strategy 
- Obstacles placed across the map for added difficulty  
- Self-collision system (cannot cross your own path)  
- Survival-based gameplay with increasing challenge  
- Customization options for pencil color and monster appearance
- Smooth controls using keyboard input  
- Simple and clean user interface  
- Lightweight browser-based game (no installation required)  
